{"tid":914101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 Kary帶B旅行機場餵母乳","createTime":"2018-11-24T03:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T09:06:02.000Z","uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb9a4bb87aad379c3e09be2a333b723e2c1e1be","tid":914101,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"歌手吳雨霏（Kary）今年6月誕下兒子Asher後，近日開始復出工作，趁着有空閒時間，帶同兒子搭飛機去旅行，她在社交網上載於機場哺乳室親自餵母乳的照片，整個畫面充滿愛又溫馨！<br />\n<br />\n雖然帶小朋友去旅行，要預備很多物品，Kary表示認同之餘，坦言一切都值得，以英文留言：「他們提醒我們放慢腳步，我們要打破常規，記住真正重要的事情。我們不僅僅是為了建立他們的記憶，而是為了建立他們的心靈。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GO9L3XT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGO9L3XT.png&h=585a05bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223856d70f689e8bd7daa2645075229db5802e62","tid":914101,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呱"},{"pid":"11ae3da4e7b6dbfbcb4c58ae1a3c04b39fc886cd","tid":914101,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"無美感"},{"pid":"f2aab677ec2eb63b02e5e78123f53b314bfe4ef7","tid":914101,"uid":110878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f65df4fa60c7880f99469cc89dc3648bc88d92e","tid":914101,"uid":49245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT